## Red Flags (rationalization check)

Before skipping this skill, ask yourself: are any of these thoughts
running? If yes → STOP, you're rationalizing. Invoke the skill.

| Thought | Reality |
|---------|---------|
| "This is a simple question" | Questions are tasks. Check for skills. |
| "I need more context first" | Skill check comes BEFORE clarifying questions. |
| "I can just do this quickly" | Skills tell you HOW. Check first. |
| "The skill is overkill" | Simple → complex fast. Use it. |
| "I remember this pattern" | Skills evolve. Read current version. |

